Field Detail

featureMap

protected HashMap<Integer,Boolean> featureMap
This feature map contains all features of the solver. Each feature is encoded by an Integer value, that is specified for each feature in the TargetSolver interface. Solver-specific features are excluded. The HashMap HAS TO BE private, in order to let noone mess around with the features of the solver.

setFeature

public void setFeature(char feature,
                       boolean turnOn)
Description copied from interface: TargetSolver
Set the feature of a solver to true or false (i.e. turn it on(true) or off (false)). Features can only be turned on if they are supported. It is also not possible to add NEW features with this method - Only features intitiated in the constructor and that are supported, can be modified.
